.SH "DESCRIPTION"
\fBDESCRIPTION\fR
.sp 2
Return the record that current cursor currently point to.
.SH "Examples"
\fBExamples\fR
.sp 2
Select records with the value of "age" greater than 10 in the
collection "bar" and return the record that current cursor
currently point to.
.sp 2
db.foo.bar.find({age:{$gt:10}}).current()
